data.description: You just found the one! A beautiful large move-in ready home nestled in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Emerald Point. It is the perfect place to set down your roots with its spacious layout and large backyard. The living room is showered in natural light, thanks to all the windows in every direction.  The first dining area is spacious and can comfortably accommodate a large dining table, perfect for memorable meals and special occasions.  The second dining breakfast area is also perfect for the cozy Sunday breakfasts that are prepared in the kitchen with ample counterspace.  The house offers 4 well-appointed bedrooms, each providing a serene oasis for relaxation and walk-in closets. The master suite is a true retreat, boasting a generous layout, a walk-in closet, and a private en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, accommodating various needs and preferences. Rest easy knowing the roof is fairly new at just 3 years old and the AC system was just upgraded to include a Blue UV-Light Hygienic System.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a spacious and move-in ready house in a fantastic neighborhood. Schedule your showing today and experience the charm and comfort this home has to offer!
